c=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #5649<br />\nGladiclus <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #48442 (熱血藍絲)<br />\ndewi👿 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #34103<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n叧加不正常人類list:<br />\n蔣介石（翻生）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #2436<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n部分已加入編號，另外編號後面嘅括號代表別名或者舊名，有啲可能已經改咗名，大家要提防list入面嘅人，希望有更多巴絲補充<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如有寃枉，請大家多多指正，本人有錯即改！<br />\n<br />\n為免有支那人混淆名單誤導大家，名單紀錄只以我「1000歳（人瑞）」為準</span>"},{"pid":"b20263d5edfe90b0a49f2f57b9c04f7083a77fed","tid":492842,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T09:27:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d2fb9f332ae4cc7cffc9388f754e9d6e3ba4f60","tid":492842,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb72002e9b65dfaeaba4b40a66a68dab5ca94a79","tid":492842,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T10:47:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>見到濕同志嘅意志由人瑞繼承咗，相信濕同志嘅在天之靈會得到安慰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人瑞條金剛棒仲煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">屌你老母成班死五毛食塞米啦！</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">個人簽名<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n我喺時事台整條五毛list以正視聽屌你老母連生你就搬去站務台，你咁搞咩意思啊？我屌你老母五毛「民國復興」bam完又復出又係咩意思啊？<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家五毛改名扮其他人講嘢，明顯係離間分化策略，連生你郁都唔郁下佢地！</span>頂你個肺連生竟然殺忠良不殺奸臣！屌你老母仆街冚家鏟連生包庇五毛，助紂為虐！為虎作倀！天理不容！<br />\n<br />\n我正大光明！做嘅所有嘢全部都係想杜絕五毛！你連狗兼成班濕鳩契弟管理員，竟然夠膽移走我地對抗五毛嘅post！反而民國復興，三色貓，JR嗰班五毛又唔ban走！助他人志氣滅自己威風！我話你聽死連狗你再咁搞落去連登只會步高，登後塵比五毛完全攻陷！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（請廣傳）<br />\n五毛/假膠一律統稱支那人<br />\n<br />\n假膠唔係五毛，但就做緊五毛一樣嘅事，以前大事大非面前絕對唔會玩嘢，但宜家佢地咩時候都仲扮鬼扮馬，搞到分唔清邊個打邊個，佢地已經走火入魔，所以喺以後逢見假膠請一律認作五毛處理<br />\n<br />\n由於支那人再次泛濫，現列出部分人渣名錄，比大家留意返相關人渣，如有遺漏希望大家增補，對抗支那人一齊努力<br />\n<br />\n最新名錄(定期更新)：<br />\n毛澤東 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #90863<br />\n三色貓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #46644<br />\n民國復興 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #92178（夢醒時分）&lt;-已bam<br />\nnewlife🤓🤓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #13816<br />\n游B(破產) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #51904<br />\nJR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #86841<br />\n潮吹口爆糖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #3066<br />\n講讀酒久<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#62391 (精神錯亂最佳代表)<br />\n兔仔有愛情嗎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #58099(高葵株式會社)<br />\n大鵬金翅神將 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #64806<br />\n韓國歐巴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#103440<br />\n優美開始 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #53223<br />\nRedBaron <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#85163<br />\n-李尋歡- <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#67878 (小李探花李尋歡)<br />\n高登色狼 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#14482<br />\n国語好手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #50533（香港鍵國&lt;-精英連登仔）<br />\n角大不角細 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#72990<br />\n一齊攬炒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #33874<br />\n西門慶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> #102056<br /